  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378620/extras/5828afdd4d30c69db05f61c202c9be14.poster.avif?t=1770196035\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378620/extras/5828afdd4d30c69db05f61c202c9be14.webm?t=1770196035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Become Agent 70 and stop the anomalies threatening to destroy the balance of the world!</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  Use extraordinary anomaly weapons to toss your opponents around! Overcome your enemies using melee techniques or deadly firearms!<br><br></li><li>  Modify your gameplay by upgrading your character in different ways.<br><br></li><li>  Escape your pursuers with acrobatic moves.<br><br></li><li>  Shape how the story unfolds. Unravel the mysteries you face and make the world a safer place... or plunge it into disaster.</li></ul><br> With memorable characters, unique Anomaly Bosses, a story full of twists, and smooth gameplay, Anomaly Agent is an adventure to be savored. We hope you enjoy your journey!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378620/extras/9f526fb1d1b32ffd51842de67439c268.poster.avif?t=1770196035\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378620/extras/9f526fb1d1b32ffd51842de67439c268.webm?t=1770196035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
